parameters.name: DIJobId
parameters.description: This parameter is deprecated. Use the Id parameter instead.

parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: The ID of the synchronization task.

parameters.name: NodeType
parameters.description:
The type of the node. This parameter is applicable only to the tasks that are run on serverless resource groups. Valid values:

*   **MASTER**: the master node, which is used to query the logs of JobManagers.
*   **WORKER**: the worker node, which is used to query the logs of TaskManagers.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number of the pagination query. The value is a positive integer greater than or equal to 1.
